o%2Fmsid-111444498%2Cimgsize-82812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Frohit-sharmas-unseen-reaction-before-suryakumar-yadavs-t20-world-cup-final-heart-stopping-catch-goes-viral-watch%2Farticleshow%2F111444500.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20appeared%20to%20lose%20all%20hope%20as%20he%20watched%20the%20ball%20soar%20towards%20the%20long-off%20stands.%20In%20a%20viral%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Rohit%20can%20be%20seen%20dropping%20to%20his%20knee%20as%20the%20ball%20flies%20into%20the%20air%2C%20believing%20it%20to%20be%20a%20six.%20But%20a%20calm%20and%20composed%20Suryakumar%20leaped%2C%20caught%20the%20ball%2C%20released%20it%20just%20as%20he%20went%20over%20the%20boundary%20ropes%2C%20and%20then%20came%20back%20in%20to%20complete%20a%20breathtaking%20catch.%20Witnessing%20Suryakumar's%20incredible%20effort%2C%20Rohit%20looked%20ecstatic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShe%20Can't%20Speak%2C%20Can%20Only%20Cry%26quot%3B%3A%20Family%20Looks%20For%20Daughter%20After%20Stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHathras%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20made%20headlines%C2%A0%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20for%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20Dalit%20woman%2C%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20again.%20This%20time%20for%20a%20stampede%20at%20a%20religious%20programme%20that%20has%20cost%20116%20lives.%20The%20tragedy%20is%20still%20unfolding%20and%20many%20of%20the%20devotees%20are%20desperately%20looking%20for%20lost%20family%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%2C%20a%20survivor%20of%20the%20stampede%2C%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20here%20with%20my%20family%20from%20Badaun.%20My%20brother's%20wife%20is%20missing.%20We%20got%20to%20know%20that%20several%20people%20are%20missing.%20I%20made%20announcements%20in%20the%20mic%20but%20it%20did%20not%20help%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20missing%20is%20a%2015-year-old%20named%20Chaya%2C%20whose%20family%20came%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20satsang%20from%20Agra.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20looking%20all%20over%20for%20her.%20My%20daughter%20cannot%20speak.%20She%20can%20only%20cry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20her%20anguished%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20six%20to%20seven%20people%20who%20came%2C%20my%20daughter%20is%20missing...%20No%20one%20told%20us%20where%20she%20was%2C%20they%20said%20she%20was%20here%20and%20there%20but%20I%20couldn't%20find%20her.%20The%20police%20said%20they%20don't%20know%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20have%20their%20hands%20full.%20Visuals%20from%20the%20local%20Community%20Health%20Centre%20showed%20bodies%20still%20being%20brought%20in%20buses%20and%20tempos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satsang%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20a%20local%20guru%2C%20Bhole%20Baba%20aka%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari.%20After%20it%20ended%2C%20people%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20until%20his%20car%20left%2C%20causing%20a%20huge%20build-up%20of%20people%20in%20a%20small%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20were%20on%20the%20road%2C%20who%20didn't%20move%20when%20the%20satsang%20was%20over.%20A%20crowd%20had%20gathered%20and%20people%20were%20pushing%20each%20other.%20A%20wire%20broke%20and%20people%20were%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20eyewitnesses%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20number%20of%20attendees%20is%20also%20a%20key%20factor.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20applying%20for%20permission%2C%20the%20organisers%20had%20said%20they%20were%20expecting%20around%2080%2C000%20people.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20attendees%20was%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%