0marketplace%20that%2C%20if%20used%20properly%2C%20can%20help%20directors%20and%20producers%20navigate%20the%20murky%20world%20of%20movie%20financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20objective%20is%20to%20entice%20international%20territories%20to%20agree%20to%20distribute%20a%20movie%20long%20before%20they%20see%20a%20single%20frame%20of%20it.%20This%20is%20called%20presales%2C%20and%20it%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20connections%20and%20a%20recognizable%20face%20to%20sell%20the%20project%20convincingly.%20Who%20better%20than%20Costner%20to%20pull%20that%20off%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostner%20began%20this%20process%20at%20the%202023%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20when%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2023%2F10%2Fkevin-costner-western-movie-horizon-american-saga-afm-sales-deals-1235582091%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrought%20on%20German-based%20sales%20firm%20K5%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20handle%20the%20foreign%20sales%20for%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20Chapters%201%20and%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Chapter%201%20of%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20Cannes%20in%20May%202024%2C%20the%20firm%20had%20sold%20out%20most%20of%20the%20international%20territories%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fkevin-costner-horizon-an-american-saga-cannes-1236007554%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Variety%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20producer%20familiar%20with%20foreign%20sales%20who%20asked%20to%20speak%20anonymously%20told%20BI%20that%20that%20money%20more%20than%20likely%20recouped%20Costner's%20%2438%20million%20investment%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20that%20%2430%20million%20marketing%20price%20tag%20Costner%20and%20his%20backers%20are%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20is%20separate%20from%20the%20%2438%20million%20figure%2C%20Costner%20isn't%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce83f3b8-a045-491c-a55e-2b83f5fc2680%5C%22%3ECostner%20gets%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20the%20movie's%20box%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20presales%20are%20great%2C%20but%20because%20this%20movie%20is%20an%20American%20Western%2C%20a%20genre%20that%20historically%20doesn't%20translate%20well%20overseas%2C%20Costner%20can't%20expect%20huge%20box%20office%20returns%20internationally.%20That's%20why%20he%20has%20to%20make%20sure%20to%20get%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20domestic%20grosses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fkevin-costner-horizon-stakes-box-office-career-1236056644%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%20Bros.%20reportedly%20only%20taking%208%25%20of%20grosses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20studio%20essentially%20has%20a%20service%20deal%20with%20Costner%3A%20Costner%20gets%20his%20cut%20of%20the%20box%20office%20grosses%20starting%20the%20first%20day%20the%20movie%20is%20out%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20once%20the%20film%20turns%20a%20profit.%20Doing%20the%20math%2C%20that%20means%20that%20for%20every%20%2410%20million%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20makes%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20Costner%20and%20his%20investors%20see%20%244.6%20million%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20to%20recoup%20the%20%2430%20million%20Costner%20invested%20in%20marketing%20the%20first%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20movie%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20make%20north%20of%20%2465%20million%20domestically.%20(Right%20now%2C%20it's%20made%20%2411%20million.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20even%20started%20talking%20about%20profit%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241e83c85-9283-4ac5-9892-1bc1471f9349%5C%22%3ECostner%20needs%20a%20huge%20%26quot%3BPay%201%26quot%3B%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Costner%20in%20a%20cowboy%20hat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66829eb31f0c1cd6d7301eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Costner%20in%20%26quot%3BHorizon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECostner%20believes%20in%20the%20long%20game.%20When%20he%20made%20the%20box%20office%20bomb%20%26quot%3BWaterworld%26quot%3B%20back%20in%201995%2C%20which%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20movie%20ever%20made%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20took%20ancillary%20deals%20like%20paid%20cable%20and%20DVD%20sales%20to%20finally%20break%20even.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fscottmendelson%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2Fwaterworld-starring-kevin-costner-was-the-biggest-box-office-bomb-that-wasnt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20took%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDVD%20sales%20have%20fallen%20off%20the%20map%20since%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%20so%20Costner%20can't%20lean%20into%20that.%20Instead%2C%20he'll%20have%20to%20land%20a%20major%20deal%20with%20a%20streamer%20or%20cable%20company%20for%20the%20movie's%20post-theatrical%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20%26quot%3BPay%201.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPay%201%20deals%20kick%20in%20after%20a%20movie%20is%20through%20with%20its%20Video-On-Demand%20option.%20Deals%20can%20range%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20to%20as%20high%20as%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20pay%20varies%2C%20the%20producer%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20Costner%20could%20negotiate%20a%20deal%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20because%20of%20his%20star%20power%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20franchise%20and%20not%20just%20the%20first%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20sweetens%20the%20pot%20for%20a%20streamer%20is%20that%20Costner%20is%20a%20fixture%20in%20Westerns.%20As%20the%20face%20of%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%2C%26quot%3B%20(at%20least%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyellowstone-timeline-of-controversy-criticism-conflict-kevin-costner-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eun