0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-six-day-workweek-longer-productivity-retail-agriculture-service-employees-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-day%20workweek%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20industries%20to%20boost%20productivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%2048-hour%20workweek%20counters%20global%20trends%20toward%20shorter%20ones%20for%20better%20productivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECritics%20argue%20longer%20hours%20may%20lead%20to%20burnout%2C%20despite%20higher%20pay%20for%20additional%20workdays.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20long%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhelpful-advice-for-following-a-mediterranean-diet-from-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esiga%20siga%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Greek%20phrase%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bslowly%2C%20slowly%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20the%20relaxed%20pace%20of%20life%20in%20the%20country%20famous%20for%20its%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20and%20clear%20Mediterranean%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20harder%20for%20some%20workers%20to%20embrace%20that%20philosophy%20as%20the%20country%20prepares%20to%20shift%20to%20a%20six-day%20workweek%20for%20some%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Greek%20government%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjul%2F01%2Fgreece-introduces-growth-oriented-six-day-working-week%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20a%2048-hour%20workweek%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20start%20Monday%2C%20could%20boost%20productivity%20amid%20a%20declining%20population%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20skilled%20workers.%20The%20shift%20is%20notable%20because%20it%20runs%20counter%20to%20the%20companies%20and%20countries%20that%20are%20experimenting%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-could-be-here-sooner-than-you-think-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour-day%20workweek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20longer%20hours%20can%20help%20people%20further%20refine%20their%20skills%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20decreased%20productivity%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.iza.org%2Fdp10722.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efatigue%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20burnout%2C%20research%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20hours%20will%20come%20with%20a%2040%25%20jump%20in%20pay%20for%20Greek%20workers%20who%20add%20two%20hours%20to%20their%20day%20or%20take%20on%20an%20extra%20eight-hour%20workday.%20The%20change%2C%20which%20won%20approval%20in%20September%2C%20applies%20to%20workers%20in%20industries%20like%20agriculture%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20various%20service%20industries%2C%20as%20BI%20previously%20reported.%20It%20also%20applies%20to%20private%20businesses%20that%20operate%2024%20hours%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20bump%20in%20pay%20for%20the%20extra%20time%2C%20some%20union%20officials%20are%20decrying%20the%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20no%20sense%20whatsoever%2C%26quot%3B%20Akis%20Sotiropoulos%2C%20from%20the%20civil%20servants'%20union%20Adedy%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20almost%20every%20other%20civilized%20country%20is%20enacting%20a%20four-day%20week%2C%20Greece%20decides%20to%20go%20the%20other%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f876f4f-8d93-41e1-af11-7e1266033d55%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoing%20more%20with%20less%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExperiments%20with%20the%20four-day%20workweek%20have%20often%20shown%20being%20on%20the%20job%20for%20less%20time%20makes%20workers%20more%20productive%20because%20they're%20better%20rested%2C%20more%20focused%2C%20and%20have%20more%20time%20to%20attend%20to%20needs%20that%20arise%20in%20their%20personal%20lives%20outside%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20study%20that%20examined%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%20found%20that%20when%20overtime%20increased%20by%2010%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F241684896_Are_long_hours_reducing_productivity_in_manufacturing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%20dropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202%25%20to%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20review%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.journals.uchicago.edu%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1086%2F721803%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexamined%20the%20output%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20skilled%20workers%20at%20a%20large%20tech%20company%20in%20India%20working%20from%20home.%20When%20time%20on%20the%20clock%20went%20up%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20jump%20of%2018%25%20outside%20normal%20work%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20output%20slipped%2C%20and%20productivity%20dropped%20between%208%25%20and%2019%25.%20The%20biggest%20culprit%3A%20more%20time%20spent%20communicating%20and%20coordinating%20and%20less%20time%20engaging%20in%20uninterrupted%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20shows%20workers%20often%20benefit%20when%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-stress-burnout-work-mental-health-professional-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20away%20from%20their%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20more%20free%20time%20can%20also%20boost%20gratitude%20among%20employees.%20Zachary%20Toth%20runs%20a%20small%20manufacturing%20company%20in%20Toronto.%20He%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20and%20his%20management%20colleagues%20began%20looking%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-day-workweek-companies-profits-workers-happier-efficient-takano-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour-day%20workweek%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20successful%20pilots%20in%20Japan%20and%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToth%20didn't%20expect%20the%20extra%20time%20away%20from%20the%20factory%20would%20encourage%20workers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-day-workweek-workers-showed-up-on-weekends-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshow%20up%20without%20being%20asked%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20just%20came%20in%20because%20they%20knew%20there%20was%20a%20project%20that%20had%20to%20be%20finished%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20want%20productivity%20to%20fall.%20They%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20keep%20doing%20the%20four-day%20workweek%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToth%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20president%20of%20Metex%20Corporation%2C%20said%20productivity%20has%20increased%20%26quot%3Bin%20every%20single%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasis%20Technologies%2C%20an%20advertising%20software%20company%2C%20shifted%20its%20workweek%20to%20four%20and%20a%20half%20days%20after%20years%20of%20experiments%20with%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20and%20other%20approaches.%20For%202024%2C%20it%20settled%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-us-half-day-fridays-pros-and-cons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20Fridays%20a%20half%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Barron%2C%20the%20company's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20talent%20and%20development%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20had%20been%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20give%20workers%20more%20time%20to%20decompress%20while%20still%20meeting%20the%20business's%20needs.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20half-day%20approach%20is%20best%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20is%20intended%20for%20people%20to%20take%20a%20mental%20break%2C%20to%20get%20caught%20up%2C%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20go%20to%20that%20workout%20class%20that%20they%20couldn't%20get%20to%20at%207%3A30%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Barron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22209c66e4-f60d-4e56-b0fc-57bb7401dc19%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%205-day%20week%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Greece%2C%20the%20longer%20workweek%20is%20designed%20to%20address%20changing%20demographics%2C%20which%20the%20country's%20prime%20minister%2C%20Kyriakos%20Mitsotakis%2C%20has%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bticking%20timebomb%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Guardian.%20Some%20500%2C000%20largely%20young%20and%20educated%20Greek%20citizens%20have%20left%20the%20country%20following%20a%20debt%20crisis%20that%20began%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rule%20is%20voluntary%2C%20but%20some%20critics%20say%20it%20will%20effectively%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20a%20five-day%20workweek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAris%20Kazakos%2C%20an%20emeritus%20labor%20law%20professor%20at%20the%20Aristotle%20University%20of%20Thessaloniki%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgreece-introduces-the-six-day-work-week%2Fa-69439050%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEmployers%2520can%2520instruct%2520staff%2520to%2Cthe%2520sixth%2520day%2520of%2520labor.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Germany's%20DW%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20outlet%20that%20bosses%20can%20require%20workers%20to%20work%20a%20sixth%20day%2C%20and%20workers%20can't%20say%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20six%20days%20%26quot%3Bwill%20kill%20off%20the%20five-day%20workweek%20for%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-six-day-workweek-productivity-plan-may-not-work-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719949507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66843d73268f62ba18a6ce04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-six-day-workweek-productivity-plan-may-not-work-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20to%20a%20six-day%20workweek%20for%20some%20industries%20in%20Greece%20aims%20to%20increase%20productivity%2C%20but%20it%20could%20do%20the%20opposite.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58