ims%2C%20dead%20or%20unconscious%2C%20of%20the%20stampede%20that%20occurred%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3E'satsang'%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Phulrai%20village%2C%20were%20brought%20in%20ambulances%2C%20trucks%20and%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20sat%20crying%20among%20five%20or%20six%20bodies%20in%20a%20truck%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20help%20her%20get%20the%20body%20of%20her%20daughter%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20A%20video%20clip%20showed%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20lying%20lifeless%20in%20a%20different%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20injured%20were%20seen%20lying%20near%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20local%20government%20hospital%20surrounded%20by%20anxious%20relatives.%20Locals%20blamed%20the%20administration's%20negligence%20for%20the%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20hours%20went%20by%2C%20the%20official%20estimate%20of%20the%20fatalities%20jumped%20and%20the%20crowds%20outside%20the%20trauma%20centre%20and%20the%20mortuary%20swelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20district%20official%2C%20116%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%20are%20believed%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20and%20several%20more%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20almost%20100-200%20casualties%20and%20there%20was%20only%20one%20doctor%20at%20the%20hospital.%20There%20was%20no%20facility%20for%20oxygen.%20Some%20are%20still%20breathing%20but%20there%20are%20no%20proper%20treatment%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20agitated%20youth%20said%20outside%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyewitness%20Shakuntala%20Devi%20told%20PTI%20Videos%20that%20the%20stampede%20took%20place%20while%20people%20were%20leaving%20the%20venue%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E'satsang'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BOutside%2C%20there%20was%20a%20road%20built%20on%20a%20height%20over%20a%20drain.%20People%20fell%20atop%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stampede%20apparently%20occurred%20due%20to%20overcrowding%2C%20the%20Sikandra%20Rao%20police%20station%20SHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20government%20has%20formed%20a%20team%20comprising%20the%20Agra%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%20and%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%20of%20Aligarh%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20media%20persons%2C%20District%20Magistrate%20Ashish%20Kumar%20said%20it%20was%20a%20private%20function%20for%20which%20the%20permission%20was%20granted%20by%20the%20sub-divisional%20magistrate.%20The%20local%20administration%20provided%20security%20outside%20the%20venue%20while%20the%20internal%20arrangement%20was%20to%20be%20looked%20after%20by%20the%20organisers%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20expressed%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20and%20instructed%20officials%20to%20reach%20the%20accident%20site%20and%20carry%20out%20relief%20measures.%20He%20announced%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20ex%20gratia%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20dead%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20said%20an%20FIR%20will%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20also%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20arrange%20for%20proper%20treatment%20of%20those%20injured%20and%20immediately%20take%20them%20to%20hospitals.%20He%20wished%20them%20a%20speedy%20recovery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719941040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fi478dbsg_hathras-stampede_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foutside-hathras-hospital-scattered-bodies-loud-wail