%20feats%20to%20sustainable%20urban%20planning%2C%20these%20awards%20celebrate%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranav%20Adani%2C%20Managing%20Director%20(Agro%2C%20Oil%20and%20Gas)%20and%20Director%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20delivered%20the%20keynote%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Singh%2C%20CEO%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%2C%20said%20there%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfrashakti-awards-adani-green-energy-ceo-on-how-to-find-innovators-6017861%5C%22%3Eneed%20to%20discover%20innovators%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%20to%20tap%20into%20their%20brand%20new%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20big%20country%2C%20and%20we%20have%20so%20many%20innovators%20and%20pioneers%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20India.%20They%20are%20coming%20up%20with%20brand%20new%20ideas%20which%20can%20scale%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20have%20an%20award%20function%20as%20this%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20identify%20these%20innovators%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20a%20platform%20where%20they%20meet%20and%20interact%20with%20industrialists%20and%20we%20can%20take%20that%20innovation%20and%20idea%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panelists%20at%20the%20event%20included%20Ashwani%20Gupta%2C%20CEO%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd%3B%20Anup%20Sahay%2C%20Head%2C%20Corporate%20Strategy%20and%20Special%20Initiatives%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%3B%20Mallanna%20Sasalu%2C%20CEO%2C%20Provident%20Housing%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Rumjhum%20Chatterjee%2C%20Co-founder%2C%20Infravision%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfrashakti-awards-adani-ports-ceo-on-how-to-reach-10-trillion-economy-6018131%5C%22%3ETrade%20is%20at%20the%20core%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20taking%20India's%20economy%20to%20%2410%20trillion%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20CEO%20Ashwani%20Gupta%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20Infrashakti%20Awards.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20in%20a%20%2410%20trillion%20economy.%20Where%20will%20it%20come%20from%3F%20Trade%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20is%20it%20exactly%20about%20trade%3F%20When%20we%20talk%20about%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20energy%2C%20industrialisation%20-%20all%20that%20is%20about%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20our%20figures%2C%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20trade%20last%20year%20was%20done%20by%20maritime%2C%20which%20is%2068%20per%20cent%20of%20value%20of%20all%20India...%20This%20is%20very%20clear%20and%20more%20and%20more%20efficient%20trade%2C%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20globally%2C%20is%20going%20to%20contribute%20to%20this%20%2410%20trillion%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumjhum%20Chatterjee%2C%20Co-founder%2C%20Infravision%20Foundation%20said%20the%20country%20has%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20core%20infrastructure%20sectors%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20it.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%20however%2C%20that%20we%20now%20need%20to%20put%20into%20looking%20at%20how%20we%20can%20galvanise%20social%20sectors%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panelists%20in%20the%20conversations%20on%20sustainable%20and%20climate-resilient%20infrastructure%20were%3A%20Ricky%20Kej%2C%20three-time%20Grammy%20Award%20winner%2C%20composer%20and%20environmentalist%3B%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20CEO%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%3B%20G%20Raghuram%2C%20Former%20Director%2C%20IIM%20Bangalore%3B%20Anumita%20Roychowdhury%2C%20Executive%20Director%2C%20Research%20and%20Advocacy%2C%20Centre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%2C%20and%20Vinayak%20Chatterjee%20of%20Infravision%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinayak%20Chatterjee%2C%20referring%20to%20India's%20Sustainability%20Index%2C%20gave%20two%20suggestions%20for%20policymakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20burdened%20with%20large%20historical%20installations%20of%20infrastructure%20from%20the%20colonial%20times%20-%20be%20it%20railway%20bridges%20or%20dams%20or%20tunnels.%20We%20should%20have%20strong%20inspection%20teams%20to%20keep%20that%20infrastructure%20in%20check%20so%20that%20railway%20bridges%20and%20dams%20don't%20collapse%2C%20and%20cracks%20don't%20appear%20in%20hill%20towns%20such%20as%20Joshimath%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20doesn't%20have%20a%20sustainable%20index.%20We%20at%20Infravision%20Foundation%20have%20developed%20a%20102-point%20sustainability%20index.%20Policymakers%20should%20now%20use%20this%20index%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20propagating%20it%20largely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20climate%20change%2C%20CSE's%20Anumita%20Roychowdhury%20said%20if%20there's%20a%20takeaway%20from%20the%20summer%20we%20just%20had%2C%20first%20it%20was%20the%20persistent%20heatwave%20and%20then%20unprecedented%20flood.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20telling%20us%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20real%20and%20constant%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20keep%20blaming%20climate%20change%20all%20the%20time%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20way%20infrastructure%20is%20taking%20shape%20today.%20It%20aggravates%20and%20compounds%20the%20impact%20if%20we%20don't%20get%20the%20blueprint%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicky%20Kej%20said%20development%2C%20by%20its%20definition%2C%20should%20be%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinners%20of%20the%20NDTV%20Infrashakti%20Awards%20are-%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpecial%20Award%20for%20Infrastructure%20Financier%20-%20State%20Bank%20Of%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20for%20Connecting%20India%20-%20E%20Sreedharan.%3C%2Fli%3E