%22132-Seater%20Bus%2C%20Food%20And%20Hostesses%3A%20Nitin%20Gadkari's%20Pilot%20Project%20For%20Nagpur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPollution%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20issue%20in%20India%20and%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20government%20is%20on%20promoting%20the%20use%20of%20non-polluting%20sources%20to%20power%20personal%20and%20public%20transportation%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20during%20the%20NDTV%20Infrashakti%20Awards%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20minister%20also%20said%20work%20is%20underway%20on%20a%20pilot%20project%20in%20Nagpur%20involving%20a%20132-seater%20bus%20which%20will%20have%20airplane-like%20seating%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bbus%20hostess%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20will%20run%20on%20non-polluting%20sources%20of%20energy%20while%20still%20being%20cheaper%20than%20regular%20diesel%20buses.%20The%20government's%20aim%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20for%20India%20to%20become%20a%20net%20energy%20exporter%20instead%20of%20an%20importer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20problem%20in%20the%20country%20today%20is%20pollution%20-%20air%2C%20water%20and%20sound%20-%20especially%20for%20Delhi.%20We%20need%20import-substitute%2C%20cost-effective%2C%20pollution-free%20and%20indigenous%20transport%20solutions.%20We%20have%20electric%20vehicles...%20Now%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20is%20installing%20300%20ethanol%20pumps%20and%20automobile%20companies%20are%20bringing%20in%20flex%20vehicles.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20filling%20petrol%20at%20Rs%20120%20a%20litre%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20use%20ethanol%20at%20Rs%2060%20per%20litre%2C%20with%20the%20vehicle%20running%2060%25%20on%20electricity%20and%2040%25%20on%20ethanol.%20This%20will%20also%20reduce%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20thing%20the%20government%20is%20focusing%20on%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%2C%20is%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20public%20transportation.%20A%20diesel%20bus%20costs%20Rs%20115%20a%20km%20to%20run%20while%20AC%20electric%20buses%20run%20at%20Rs%2041%20and%20non-AC%20ones%20at%20Rs%2037%2C%20with%20subsidies.%20Without%20subsidies%2C%20this%20will%20now%20be%20between%20Rs%2050%20and%20Rs%2060%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20will%20help%20reduce%20ticket%20prices%20by%2015-20%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20doing%20a%20pilot%20project%20in%20Nagpur%20with%20Tata.%20When%20I%20went%20to%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20they%20have%20a%20trolley%20bus%20which%20is%20achieved%20by%20joining%20three%20buses.%20Our%20project%20will%20seat%20132%20people%20and%20will%20travel%2049%20km%20on%20the%20ring%20road%20and%20it%20will%20halt%20at%20the%20bus%20stop%20after%2040%20km%2C%20getting%20charged%20for%20the%20next%2040%20km%20in%20just%2040%20seconds.%20The%20cost%20for%20this%20is%20working%20out%20to%20Rs%2035-40%20per%20km%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20suggested%20it%20needs%20air-conditioning%2C%20comfortable%20chairs%20and%20space%20to%20keep%20a%20laptop%20in%20front%20of%20the%20seats.%20And%2C%20like%20air%20hostesses%2C%20there%20should%20be%20bus%20hostesses%20to%20give%20people%20fruits%2C%20packed%20food%20and%20beverages.%20My%20calculation%20is%20that%20this%20bus%20will%20cost%20(to%20run)%2030%25%20less%20than%20a%20diesel%20bus.%20If%20solar%20power%20is%20used%2C%20the%20cost%20will%20go%20down%20even%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20JCB%20has%20made%20construction%20equipment%20that%20uses%2050%25%20ethanol%20and%2050%25%20CNG%20and%20tractor%20makers%20are%20also%20working%20on%20machines%20that%20run%20on%20ethanol%2C%20methanol%20and%20CNG.%20This%2C%20he%20stressed%2C%20will%20help%20not%20just%20reduce%20pollution%20but%20also%20increase%20the%20income%20of%20farmers%20substantially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEthanol%20From%20Stubble%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20Petroleum%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Puri%20for%20accepting%20his%20suggestion%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20MP%20said%20Indian%20Oil%20has%20started%20a%20project%20producing%201%20lakh%20litres%20of%20ethanol%20from%20stubble%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bio%20bitumen.%20The%20project%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20nearly%20complete%20and%20will%20also%20produce%2076%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20bio%20aviation%20fuel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20the%20ministry's%20success%20in%20another%20area%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%20it%20reduced%20the%20height%20of%20the%20mountain%20of%20waste%20in%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20in%20Delhi%20by%20seven%20metres%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Contaminated%20water%20from%20sewage%20is%20being%20purified%20and%20is%20being%20used%20in%20power%20generation.%20Organic%20waste%20can%20also%20be%20used%20to%20make%20bio%20CNG%20and%20bio%20LNG%2C%20or%20hydrogen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20drones%20and%20ropeways%20are%20also%20in%20focus%20and%20another%20area%20of%20interest%20for%20the%20ministry%20is%20funicular%20railways%20(rope-propelled%20trains%20used%20on%20steep%20cliffs)%2C%20especially%20for%20places%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20and%20Ladakh.%20All%20of%20these%20will%20help%20reduce%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGPS%20Tolling%20In%203%20Months%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20big%20announcement%2C%20the%20highways%20minister%20said%20that%20GPS-based%20tolling%2C%20which%20the%20government%20has%20been%20working%20on%20for%20a%20while%2C%20will%20be%20implemented%20on%205%2C000%20km%20of%20road%20within%20three%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTenders%20are%20ready.%20Satellite-based%20tolling%20will%20ensure%20you%20only%20pay%20for%20the%20number%20of%20km%20that%20you%20have%20travelled%20on%20a%20particular%20road%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20will%20be%20deducted%20straight%20from%20your%20bank%20account.%20You%20won't%20have%20to%20stop%20anywhere.%20This%20will%20start%20on%205%2C000%20km%20and%20will%20then%20be%20implemented%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20he%20is%20aiming%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20revolution%26quot%3B%20in%20agriculture%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20emphasised%20that%20he%20has%20no%20shortage%20of%20funds%20for%20his%20projects%20and%20investors%20are%20queuing%20up%20because%20his%20ministry%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20goldmine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20foreign%20investors%20approach%20me%2C%20I%20serve%20them%20tea%20and%20then%20my%20first%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20finance%20projects%20in%20rupees.%20If%20they%20say%20yes%2C%20I%20take%20the%20conversation%20forward%20and%20end%20it%20if%20they%20don't.%20There%20are%20rupee-dollar%20fluctuations%20and%20the%20yen%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20we%20are%20sometimes%20afraid%20of%20taking%20loans%20even%20on%20zero%20per%20cent%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719938760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6r8bhhs_nitin-gadkari_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F132-seater-bus-food-and-hostesses-nitin-gadkaris-pilot-project-for-nagpur-6019843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pollution%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20issue%20in%20India%20and%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20government%20is%20on%20promoting%20the%20use%20of%20non-polluting%20sources%20to%20power%20personal%20and%20public%20transportation%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F132-seater-bus-food-and-hostesses-nitin-gadkaris-pilot-project-for-nagpur-6019843%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F132-seater-bus-food-and-hostesses-nitin-gadkaris-pilot-project-for-nagpur-6019843%2Famp%2F1%22%2