%20the%20term%20'Hindu%20terrorism'.%20Their%20associates%20compared%20Hinduism%20to%20diseases%20like%20dengue%20and%20malaria.%20This%20country%20will%20never%20forgive%20them.%20Under%20a%20well-thought-out%20conspiracy%2C%20their%20entire%20ecosystem%20has%20made%20it%20fashionable%20to%20degrade%2C%20insult%2C%20and%20mock%20Hindu%20traditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20targetting%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20your%20culture%2C%20this%20is%20your%20character%2C%20this%20is%20your%20thinking%2C%20this%20is%20your%20hatred.%20These%20are%20the%20actions%20against%20Hindus%20in%20this%20country.%20This%20country%20will%20not%20forget%20it%20for%20centuries%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20whole%20speech%20today%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Opposition%20protests%20and%20table%20thumping%20from%20the%20background.%20Only%20the%20chants%20about%20%26quot%3BManipur%26quot%3B%20and%20justice%20changed%20to%20a%20Bollywood%20one-liner%20that%20warns%20children%C2%A0%20against%20lying%20--%20%26quot%3BJhooth%20bole%20kaua%20kaate%20(lie%20and%20you%20get%20pecked%20by%20a%20crow)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20speech%20in%20parliament%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20yesterday%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20come%20armed%20with%20photos%20of%20various%20gods%20including%20Lord%20Shiva%20and%20prophets%20from%20other%20religions%2C%20and%20used%20them%20to%20launch%20a%20sharp%20attack%20on%20PM%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20spreading%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20comments%20had%20brought%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20his%20feet.%20%26quot%3BCalling%20the%20entire%20Hindu%20society%20violent%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20said%20%E2%80%93%20a%20comment%20the%20Congress%20said%20was%20another%20example%20of%20the%20BJP%20twisting%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20PM%20Modi%20got%20a%20sharp%20retort%20from%20Mr%20Gandhi%20--%20one%20that%20was%20among%20the%20remarks%20later%20expunged%20from%20official%20records.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20brushed%20off%20the%20censorship%2C%20saying%20he%20has%20said%20what%20he%20wished%20to%20say%20and%20would%20not%20worry%20about%20whether%20they%20are%20expunged%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20yesterday%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20today.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20you%20(the%20Hindus)%20were%20disrespected.%20You%20shouldn't%20ignore%20this%20as%20a%20childish%20act.%20They%20have%20malicious%20intentions.%20Their%20lies%20question%20the%20intellect%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20insult%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20by%20the%20opposition%20is%20hurting%201.4%20billion%20people%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20taught%20since%20childhood%20that%20every%20form%20is%20a%20manifestation%20of%20God.%20No%20form%20of%20God%20exists%20for%20personal%20gain.%20The%20insult%20of%20our%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20is%20hurting%201.4%20billion%20people%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20country%20cannot%20forgive%20the%20mockery%20of%20the%20forms%20of%20God%20for%20personal%20political%20gain.%20Watching%20the%20scenes%20of%20yesterday's%20assembly%2C%20now%20Hindu%20society%20will%20have%20to%20think%20whether%20this%20is%20a%20preparation%20for%20some%20experiment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719928080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frb34e2uo_modi_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconspiracy-being-hatched-to-level-false-allegations-against-hindus-pm-modi-6018377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20w