20(Rohit)%20been%20closer%2C%20I%20would%20have%20thrown%20the%20ball%20towards%20him.%20But%20he%20was%20nowhere%20close.%20In%20those%204-5%20seconds%2C%20whatever%20happened%2C%20I%20can't%20explain.%20The%20amount%20of%20reaction%20I%20have%20been%20getting%20for%20that%2C%20people%20have%20been%20calling%2C%20messaging%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%201%2C000%20unread%20WhatsApp%20messages%20on%20my%20phone.%20The%20catch%20is%20all%20over%20social%20media.%20I'm%20grateful%20that%20I%20was%20there%20in%20those%20five%20seconds%20of%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20execution%2C%20Surya%20admitted%20that%20he%20was%20cautious%20about%20not%20touching%20the%20rope%20while%20pushing%20the%20ball%20back%20inside%20the%20ground.%20Upon%20completion%2C%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20it%20was%20a%20fair%20catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20pushed%20the%20ball%20and%20took%20the%20catch%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20hadn't%20touched%20the%20rope.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20was%20cautious%20about%20was%20that%20when%20I%20pushed%20the%20ball%20back%20inside%2C%20my%20feet%20don't%20touch%20the%20rope.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20fair%20catch.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20anything%20could%20have%20happened.%20If%20the%20ball%20had%20gone%20for%20six%2C%20the%20equation%20would%20have%20been%205%20balls%2C%2010%20runs.%20We%20might%20have%20still%20won%2C%20but%20the%20margin%20would%20have%20been%20closer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719927840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fd1dqeeto_suryakumar-catch_625x300_02_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fi-knew-i-hadnt-suryakumar-yadav-on-t20-world-cup-final-catch-amid-social-media-chatter-6015438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suryakumar%20Yadav's%20boundary-rope%20catch%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final%20was%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20turning-point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%