mp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJustice%20To%20All%2C%20Appeasement%20To%20None%20Is%20Our%20Mantra%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Top%20Quotes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20replying%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20on%20the%20President's%20address%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20asked%20MPs%20of%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20to%20follow%20the%20rules%20of%20Parliament%20and%20ensure%20that%20their%20behaviour%20on%20the%20House%20floor%20is%20exemplary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20witnessed%20a%20massive%20uproar%20in%20the%20House%20over%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks.%20The%20BJP%20accused%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20of%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20His%20remarks%20were%20expunged%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%20quotes%20from%20PM's%20speech%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Justice%20to%20all%2C%20appeasement%20to%20none%20is%20our%20mantra%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Some%20are%20hurt%20that%20they%20lost%20a%203rd%20time%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20A%20country%20becomes%20developed%20when%20aspirations%20and%20resolutions%20of%20its%20people%20are%20realised%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Our%20only%20mission%20is%20'Nation%20First'%3B%20Our%20only%20mission%20is%20'Bharat%20First'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Will%20work%2024X7%20for%202047%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Plan%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20The%20country%20is%20seeing%20our%20governance...%20ours%20is%20a%20model%20of%20'%3Cem%3ESantushtikaran%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20and%20not%20'%3Cem%3ETushtikaran'%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20When%20we%20talk%20about%20'%3Cem%3ESantushtikaran%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20it%20means%20saturation%20of%20every%20scheme%2C%20it%20means%20reaching%20the%20last%20person%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Congress%20for%20the%203rd%20time%20in%20a%20row%20could%20not%20cross%20100%20seats%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20They%20(Congress)%20are%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20narrative%20they%20they%20beat%20us%20(at%20the%20hustings)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Congress%20got%2099%2F543%2C%20not%2099%2F100%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20It's%20the%20third%20biggest%20failure%20in%20elections%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Congress%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20It's%20serious%20matter%20that%20conspiracy%20being%20hatched%20to%20level%20false%20allegations%20against%20Hindus%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Their%20allies%20compare%20Hinduism%20to%20malaria%20and%20they%20clap.%20The%20country%20will%20never%20forge%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20in%20corruption%20case%2C%20convicted%20for%20insulting%20OBC%20community%2C%20facing%20several%20defamation%20cases%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Congress%20spreading%20anarchy%20by%20its%20economic%20policies%2C%20divisive%20politics%20around%20castes%20and%20regions%2C%20questioning%20democratic%20process%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BLet's%20remember%20the%20elections%20of%201984.%20Following%20those%20elections%2C%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20were%20held%20in%20this%20country%2C%20but%20Congress%20couldn't%20even%20cross%20the%20250-mark%20even%20once.%20This%20time%20the%20Congress%20somehow%20bagged%2099%20seats%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Congress%20became%20parasitic%20party%20in%20these%20polls%2C%20its%20allies%20are%20behind%20its%20victory%20in%20most%20of%20the%2099%20seats%20it%20won%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Will%20tell%20Congress%20to%20not%20drown%20people's%20mandate%20in%20celebration%20of%20'fake%20victory'%2C%20it%20should%20accept%20people's%20mandate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20People's%20mandate%20for%20Congress%20is%20to%20sit%20where%20it%20is%2C%20in%20opposition%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20In%20third%20term%2C%20we%20will%20work%20with%20three%20times%20more%20strength%20and%20speed%2C%20and%20bring%20three%20times%20more%20results%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Congress%20opposes%20all%20those%20reforms%20that%20strengthens%20the%20country%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20