lutions%20per%20minute%20in%20the%20machine.%20Without%20any%20heating%20process%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20retain%20more%20nutrients%20and%20antioxidants%20in%20this%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20Sumila%20is%20manufacturing%2013%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328024%2Fengineer-turns-farmer-startup-tengin-makes-products-of-coconuts-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut-based%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202021%2C%20Sumila%20launched%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Greenaura%E2%80%99%20that%20sells%20products%20like%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20and%20vinegar.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354859%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sumila%20launched%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Greenaura%E2%80%99%20that%20sells%20products%20like%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20and%20vinegar.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20in%20establishing%20the%20company%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20any%20business%20background%20and%20I%20started%20from%20scratch.%20I%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20being%20a%20female%20founder.%20From%20getting%20a%20loan%20and%20permission%20to%20set%20up%20the%20unit%20to%20driving%20the%20delivery%20vehicle%20and%20raising%20awareness%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20coconut%20products%2C%20everything%20was%20a%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20her%20over%20two%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20issues%20but%20slowly%2C%20she%20started%20getting%20orders.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunching%20her%20own%20company%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Sumila.%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20I%20was%20dependent%20on%20my%20father%20for%20my%20studies%20and%20after%20my%20marriage%2C%20I%20became%20dependent%20on%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20woman%2C%20we%20need%20financial%20security%20and%20it%20was%20high%20time%20that%20I%20taste%20independence%20and%20feel%20passionate%20about%20work.%20This%20work%20has%20totally%20changed%20my%20life%20because%20prior%20to%20this%2C%20I%20never%20really%20tried%20taking%20up%20any%20job.%20Now%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20sitting%20alone%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20once%20a%20very%20shy%20person.%20I%20hesitated%20to%20speak%20in%20public.%20Now%2C%20I%20speak%20in%20universities%20and%20have%20made%20lots%20of%20contacts%20abroad.%20Last%20month%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Thailand%20for%20an%20exhibition%20under%20the%20coconut%20development%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20homemaker%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20thought%20about%20this%20life.%20It%20was%20an%20unexpected%20turning%20point%20for%20me%20and%20certainly%20it%20was%20a%20fulfill