%2Faravani-art-project-bengaluru-helps-trans-community-tackle-stigma-earn-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccess%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20compelled%20Ishnoor%20to%20begin%20thinking%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20helping%20trans%20persons%20with%20reviving%2Fstarting%20businesses.%20A%20year%20after%20this%20decision%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20Ruhaan%20Sood%20and%20Piya%20Kamal%20Sodhi%2C%20have%20extended%20help%20to%2015%20trans%20individuals%20with%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ishnoor%20Singh%20started%20project%20SoulSpectrum%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20trans%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ftrans-persons-welfare-1719563005-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354776%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIshnoor%20Singh%20started%20project%20SoulSpectrum%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20trans%20persons%20revive%20their%20businesses%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ishnoor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20help%20includes%20providing%20the%20respective%20trans%20individual%20with%20trade