1%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20on%20this%20success%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20of%20Greater%20Chennai%20Corporation%20plans%20to%20expand%20parenting%20sessions%20in%20their%20schools%2C%20anticipating%20improvements%20in%20academic%20engagement%2C%20reduced%20dropout%20rates%2C%20and%20enhanced%20mental%20health%2C%20underscoring%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20home%20environments%20in%20child%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorporate%20entities%20also%20recognise%20the%20value%20of%20parenting%20workshops%20in%20promoting%20work-life%20balance%20and%20stress%20reduction%20among%20employees.%20Schools%20similarly%20offer%20these%20workshops%20to%20empower%20parents%20in%20creating%20supportive%20home%20environments%2C%20positively%20influencing%20academic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20behavioural%20aspects%20of%20child%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20movement%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332417%2Fhow-to-fight-for-children-rights-lgbtqia-community-stories-of-acceptance-support-of-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparent%20education%20is%20pivotal%20for%20a%20family%E2%80%99s%20well-being%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20society.%20Advocating%20for%20parent%20education%20as%20an%20accessible%20fundamental%20right%20across%20all%20socio-economic%20groups%20is%20crucial.%20By%20supporting%20parents%20in%20raising%20their%20children%2C%20we%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20better%20world%20and%20a%20better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Kesang%20Menezes%20of%20Parenting%20Matters%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%3Cem%3E%20Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParenting%20Matters%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20world%20where%20children%20can%20thrive%20to%20their%20fullest%20potential.%20They%20believe%20that%20informed%20and%20connected%20parenting%20is%20crucial%20for%20individual%20growth%2C%20community%20well-being%2C%20and%20societal%20progress.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETheir%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20empower%20parents%20to%20create%20nurturing%20families.%20With%20a%20team%20of%2012%20certified%20parent%20educators%20having%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20they%20have%20transformed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%201%20lakh%20families.%20Parenting%20Matters%20equips%20parents%20with%20the%20latest%20knowledge%20and%20essential%20skills%20through%20workshops%2C%20courses%2C%20talks%2C%20and%20articles.%20They%20focus%20on%20providing%20insights%20into%20brain%20and%20child%20development%2C%20alongside%20offering%20strategies%20for%20fostering%20positive%20communication%20and%20effective%20discipline.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWorking%20with%20parents%20across%20diverse%20groups%20in%20multiple%20languages%20in%20schools%20(both%20private%20and%20government)%2C%20corporates%2C%20and%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Parenting%20Matters%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20conviction%20that%20by%20supporting%20families%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20transformation%20towards%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20caring%20community%2C%20one%20family%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719408628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parenting%20Matters%20has%20been%20working%20with%20parents%20for%20over%2020%20years%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20effective%20and%20sensitive%20ways%20to%20raise%20their%20children.%20Their%20main%20focus%20is%20to%20undo%20the%20past%20where%20anger%2C%20intolerance%2C%20and%20disrespect%20governed%20parent-children%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354393%2Fhow-to-improve-your-parenting-skills-ten-lessons-