e%20did%20not%20have%20any%20cold%20storage%20facility%20for%20vaccines.%20Having%20a%20permanent%20energy%20supply%20was%20crucial%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20non-profit%20decided%20to%20harness%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20C-NES%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114009%2Fboat-clinics-brahmaputra-healthcare-boat-clinics-switching-solar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESELCO%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20works%20to%20bring%20sustainable%20energy%20solutions%20to%20rural%20and%20urban%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20large%20boats%20were%20equipped%20with%20solar%20panels%20of%203%20KV%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20solar%20power%20can%E2%80%99t%20drive%20vessels%20on%20a%20river%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20So%2C%20we%20use%20it%20to%20run%20lighting%20and%20basic%20services%20like%20fans.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20cold%20chains%20for%20chilling%20units%20which%20store%20and%20carry%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-saving%20equipment%20are%20also%20solar-powered%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20for%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saddam%2C%20who%20remains%20in%20the%20boat%20for%20at%20least%20nine%20days%20on%20a%20stretch%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20solar-powered%20chilling%20units%20are%20very%20beneficial%20as%20without%20them%2C%20we%20could%20not%20keep%20the%20vaccines%20for%20more%20than%20three%20days.%20Besides%2C%20it%20is%20really%20helpful%20in%20running%20fans%20all%20day%20as%20it%20is%20extremely%20hot%20and%20humid%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20feel%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20should%20be%20increased%20for%20better%20results.%20Last%20night%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20fans%20could%20only%20last%20till%209%3A30.%20We%20had%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20generator%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20If%20the%20capacity%20is%20increased%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20to%20bed%20and%20sleep%20peacefully%20after%20a%20hectic%20day%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20believes%20the%20capacity%20must%20be%20increased%2C%20Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20floating%20health%20clinic%20is%20successfully%20catering%20to%20about%2010%2